fficiency are two pivotal points of success in dry bulk shipping. Liquidity is crucial in ensuring and sustaining these. Safe Bulkers, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SB\" title=\"Safe Bulkers, Inc.\">SB</a></span>) excels in these areas. Its impeccable performance and prudent investments allow it to keep</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1064904328/image_1064904328.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747451-safe-bulkers-safe-route-to-financial-stability-despite-headwinds", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 14:34:05", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747450", "title": "Banks: Rising Bond Yields Give Cause For Concern", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"rise of the treasury yield\" data-id=\"1361920704\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1276px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1361920704/image_1361920704.jpg?i