ic.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Wagner Meier/Getty Images News</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Performance Assessment</h2> <p>The Brazilian oil company Petrobras (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PBR\" title=\"Petr\u00f3leo Brasileiro S.A. - Petrobras\">PBR</a></span>) has been a bit of a miss for me since my last update 1.75 years ago as it has handily outperformed the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747448-petrobras-stock-expanding-production-at-attractive-breakeven-economics", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 14:23:48", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747444", "title": "Pfizer: A Step-By-Step Strategy Before Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture class=\"highlighted_text\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pfizer HQ in New York City\" data-id=\"1491484031\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1101px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">georgeclerk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Article Thesis</h2> <p>What a bumpy ride for Pfizer (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PFE\" title=\"Pfizer Inc.\">PFE</a></span>), one of the big pharma giants: if in 2021-2022 the market seemed to believe that COVID would last forever, catapulting the stock towards $60, today the price is not only less than half, but</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747444-pfizer-pfe-stock-step-by-step-strategy-before-earnings", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 14:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747446", "title": "PRA Group: Rebuilding Credibility And Still Undervalued", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Asian Indian businesswoman with piggy bank in the office.\" data-id=\"2180704241\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Chong Kee Siong/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It takes time to turn a business around, and often longer still to drive a turn in sentiment and regain investor trust. Such is the case with <strong>PRA Group</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PRAA\" title=\"PRA Group, Inc.\">PRAA</a></span>), as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180704241/image_2180704241.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747446-pra-group-stock-rebuilding-credibility-still-undervalued", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 13:51:13", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747445", "title": "Waste Management: Time To Buy The Dip", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman working in a recycling factory\" data-id=\"957987754\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1070px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">andresr</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/cappuccino-finance/analysis?ticker=WM\">Waste Management</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WM\" title=\"Waste Management, Inc.\">WM</a></span>) is an industry leader in the waste collection and disposal industry. Partnering with their customers and communities throughout the North America, they manage and reduce waste, while recovering valuable resources and creating renewable energy. Waste Management</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/957987754/image_957987754.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747445-waste-management-time-to-buy-the-dip", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 13:36:23", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747442", "title": "Microchip Technology May Not Be Addressing The Correct Issues", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Electronics workers in clean room assembling electronic components\" data-id=\"556415353\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5242px\" height=\"3932px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415353/image_556415353.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-wi